Current Problem (What You're Saying):
❌ "Press V to talk" - Who knows to press V?

❌ Say "Brittney" first - Why? Just let me talk!

❌ Type commands in a chat box - That feels like coding

❌ Keyboard shortcuts (Ctrl+Z, H, 1-5) - Too technical

Better Solution:
✅ Big obvious [🎤 Record] button - Click once, talk, click again when done

✅ No wake words - Just say what you want immediately

✅ Visual buttons for everything - "Add NPC," "Add Room," etc.

✅ Pre-made templates - 80% of people want the same things

✅ Guided wizard - Step-by-step for beginners

Real World Comparison:
Current Hololand = Like using GitHub

